he%20next%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sinha%2C%20who%20is%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20headed%20by%20Ms%20Banerjee%2C%20made%20the%20statement%20in%20response%20to%20a%20query%20as%20to%20how%20he%20saw%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20as%20a%20prospective%20Prime%20Ministerial%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20would%20be%20very%20good%20for%20the%20country%20that%20at%20a%20time%20when%20we%20also%20have%20a%20woman%20as%20the%20President%2C%20we%20had%20a%20woman%20as%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20too.%20A%20firebrand%20leader%20like%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20who%20has%20a%20mass%20base%2C%20would%20fit%20the%20bill%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20PTI%20in%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sinha%2C%20who%20represents%20Asansol%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20however%2C%20hastened%20to%20add%20%26quot%3Bwho%20would%20be%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20is%20a%20decision%20that%20would%20be%20taken%20at%20an%20appropriate%20time.%20My%20point%20is%20to%20underscore%20that%20we%2C%20in%20INDIA%2C%20have%20no%20dearth%20of%20talent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20youth%20icon%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20in%20whom%20the%20nation%20sees%20its%20future.%20We%20have%20the%20modern%20day%20Chanakya%20-%20Sharad%20Pawar.%20And%20of%20course%2C%20we%20have%20firebrand%20mass%20leader%20Mamata%20Banerjee.%20In%20contrast%2C%20the%20BJP-led%20NDA%20has%20none%20except%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%26quot%3B%20asserted%20the%20actor-turned-politician.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sinha%2C%20who%20quit%20the%20BJP%20four%20years%20ago%20and%20remained%20with%20the%20Congress%20for%20a%20brief%20period%20before%20joining%20the%20Trinamool%2C%20also%20asserted%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20does%20not%20behove%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20mock%20our%20alliance%20with%20the%20use%20of%20terms%20like%20'ghamandia'%20(proud).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20speaks%20of%20issues%20like%20corruption%20and%20nepotism%20to%20criticize%20the%20opposition%20coalition.%20As%20a%20former%20NDA%20insider%2C%20I%20wager%20that%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20allies%20are%20second%20to%20none%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20nepotism.%20And%20their%20stand%20on%20corruption%20got%20exposed%20when%20they%20allied%20with%20those%20accused%20of%20corruption%20in%20Maharashtra%20by%20the%20PM%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Sinha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20flying%20kiss%20controversy%2C%20Mr%20Sinha%20said%20he%20was%20surprised%20at%20the%20allegation%20levelled%20against%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20by%20Union%20minister%20Smriti%20Irani%20%26quot%3Bwho%20respects%20me%20a%20lot%20as%20a%20senior%20in%20the%20acting%20profession%2C%20though%20unlike%20me%2C%20she%20never%20made%20it%20to%20films%20and%20remained%20confined%20to%20TV%20serials.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20too%20was%20present%20in%20the%20House%20at%20the%20time.%20No%20such%20gesture%20was%20made.%20I%20wonder%20why%20Irani%2C%20who%20has%20matured%20over%20the%20years%2C%20made%20such%20an%20allegation%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20superstar%20of%20yesteryears%2C%20adding%2C%20with%20a%20hint%20of%20mischief%2C%20the%20Urdu%20couplet%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Ekuchh%20tho%20majbooriyan%20rahi%20hongi%2C%20yunhi%20koi%20bewafa%20nahin%20hota%20%3C%2Fem%3E(there%20must%20have%20been%20some%20pressing%20compulsions%2C%20one%20does%20not%20become%20unfaithful%20just%20like%20that)%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Patna%20Sahib%20MP%2C%20who%20represented%20the%20seat%20covering%20his%20home%20town%20for%20two%20consecutive%20terms%2C%20until%20losing%20it%20in%202019%2C%20asserted%20that%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20and%20his%20deputy%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20were%20%26quot%3Babsolutely%20right%26quot%3B%20in%20taking%20exception%20to%20PM%20Modi's%20claim%20that%20a%20new%20AIIMS%20has%20been%20set%20up%20in%20Darbhanga.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20deplored%20PM%20Modi's%20'khooni%