ider.com%2Fchatgpt-jobs-at-risk-replacement-artificial-intelligence-ai-labor-trends-2023-02%5C%22%3EChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20a%20neat%20little%20trick%20to%20convince%20people%20it's%20smart%3A%20A%20kind%20of%20style%20over%20substance%20approach.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearchers%20from%20Purdue%20University%20analyzed%20ChatGPT's%20replies%20to%20517%20questions%20posted%20to%20Stack%20Overflow%2C%20an%20essential%20Q%26amp%3BA%20site%20for%20software%20developers%20and%20engineers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20assessing%20the%20bot's%20responses%20for%20%26quot%3Bcorrectness%2C%20consistency%2C%20comprehensiveness%2C%20and%20conciseness%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20researchers%20found%20that%2052%25%20of%20the%20answers%20were%20flat-out%20incorrect%2C%20and%2077%25%20committed%20the%20writing%20sin%20of%20being%20verbose.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farxiv.org%2Fpdf%2F2308.02312.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAn%20additional%20segment%20of%20the%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20ChatGPT%20users%20prefer%20its%20responses%20to%20questions%20versus%20the%20human%20responses%20on%20Stack%20Overflow%20a%20startling%2040%25%20of%20the%20time%20%E2%80%94%20despite%20all%20the%20errors%20it%20throws%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20asked%20why%20they%20preferred%20ChatGPT%20answers%20even%20when%20they%20were%20incorrect%2C%20participants%20suggested%20the%20comprehensiveness%20and%20articulated%20language%20structures%20of%20the%20answers%20to%20be%20some%20reason%20for%20their%20preference%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20research%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20caveat%3A%20This%20user%20analysis%20involved%20just%2012%20programmers%20being%20asked%20to%20assess%20if%20they%20prefer%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-use-get-better-chatgpt-ai-prompt-guide%5C%22%3Eresponses%20of%20ChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20those%20written%20by%20humans%20on%20Stack%20Overflow%20to%202%2C000%20randoml