ps%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F241-wasim-jaffer-playerprofile%5C%22%3EWasim%20Jaffer%3C%2Fa%3E%20called%20Hardik's%20poor%20batting%20a%20%26quot%3Bconcern%26quot%3B%20and%20stated%20that%20it%20looked%20%26quot%3Brusty%26quot%3B%20as%20the%20all-rounder%20was%20not%20free-flowing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWell%2C%20it%20has%20been%20a%20concern.%20He%20looks%20little%20rusty.%20We%20can't%20see%20that%20the%20free-flowing%20Hardik%20Pandya%20who%20comes%20in%20and%20strikes%20it%20sweetly.%20Doesn't%20mean%20hitting%20sixes%20but%20striking%20it%20nicely%2C%20rotating%20the%20strike.%20Apart%20from%20the%20fifty%20he%20scored%20in%20the%203rd%20ODI%2C%20where%20also%20he%20started%20very%20very%20slowly%2C%20and%20picked%20it%20up%20in%20the%20slog%20overs.%20But%20even%20then%20he%20looked%20a%20little%20rusty%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.espncricinfo.com%2Fcricket-videos%2Fthe-way-hardik-pandya-has-batted-is-a-big-concern-says-wasim-jaffer-1392439%5C%22%3Esaid%20Jaffer%20on%20ESPNCricinfo.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20a%20concern%20for%20me.%20Looking%20at%20how%20Hardik%20Pandya%20batted%20in%20the%20series%2C%20that%20was%20a%20big%20concern.%20Not%20every%20time%20he%20is%20going%20to%20start%20slowly%2C%20and%20he%20is%20going%20to%20finish%20strongly.%20We%20could%20see%20this%20during%20this%20series%20as%20well.%20As%20soon%20as%20he%20comes%2C%20the%20momentum%20drops%20down%2C%20the%20strike-rate%20comes%20down%20and%20puts%20the%20pressure%20on%20the%20other%20guys%20and%20the%20dug%20out%20as%20well.%20Something%20for%20him%20to%20worry%2C%20take%20note%20and%20improve%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20series%2C%20Hardik%20stated%20that%20he%20failed%20to%20capitalize%20on%20the%20situation%20during%20the%20fifth%20T20I%20as%20Team%20India%20was%20restricted%20to%20165%2F9%20in%2020%20overs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20lost%20the%20mom