She%20noticed%20an%20editing%20category%20on%20the%20freelance%20platform%2C%20an%20area%20where%20she%20had%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaight%2C%20a%20mom%20of%20two%20teenagers%20in%20Eugene%2C%20Oregon%2C%20has%20now%20been%20freelancing%20through%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Df08990d500cd0c71d51d6efac1e6c9783671c1cf58b942fb999a558548444efa%26postID%3D64bae1d475976ff3ff4b060e%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.fiverr.com%252Feditornancy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFiverr%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%202014.%20She%20left%20the%20magazine%20and%20other%20side%20hustles%20a%20few%20years%20later%20to%20focus%20on%20freelance%20editing%20full%20time.%20She%20pursued%20freelance%20work%20in%20part%20because%20she%20wanted%20to%20be%20an%20involved%20parent%2C%20such%20as%20taking%20her%20daughters%20to%20their%20activities%2C%20and%20because%20she%20was%20taking%20care%20of%20her%20father%20who%20was%20dying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20extremely%20overwhelmed%20being%20pulled%20in%20so%20many%20directions%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20two%20young%20girls%2C%20and%20I'm%20the%20only%20parent.%20So%20it%20just%20made%20sense.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20freelancing%20meant%20schedule%20flexibility%20so%20that%20she%20could%20take%20her%20father%20to%20his%20%26quot%3Bmany%20medical%20appointments%2C%20and%20to%20get%20my%20young%20daughters%20to%20school%20and%20to%20their%20after-school%20activities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20never%20had%20to%20miss%20a%20dance%20performance%20or%20a%20gymnastic%20event%20because%20I%20had%20to%20be%20at%20work%20%E2%80%94%20I%20simply%20organized%20my%20work%20schedule%20around%20my%20personal%20life%20instead%20of%20the%20other%20way%20around%2C%26quot%3B%20Haight%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20has%20over%204%2C000%20five-star%20reviews%20on%20her%20Fiverr%20profile%3B%20completed%20at%20least%20100%20orders%20for%20several%20different%20months%20in%202020%20and%20completed%20over%207%2C000%20orders%20since%20becoming%20a%20freelancer%20on%20the%20platform%3B%20and%20has%20customers%20return%20for%20more%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Haight%20didn't%20feel%20comfortable%20disclosing%20her%20earnings%20for%20this%20article%2C%20she%20said%20she's%20%26quot%3Bconstantly%20thankful%20for%20what%20I've%20been%20able%20to%20build%20with%20my%20freelance%20business%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20that%20she%20had%20quick%20success%20on%20the%20platform.%20She%20has%20also%20been%20able%20to%20go%20on%20trips%20with%20her%20daughters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%20of%20the%20interview%C2%A0in%20July%2C%20Haight%20said%20her%20family%20just%20went%20on%20a%20cruise%20and%20were%20going%20to%20New%20York%20soon.%20She%20said%20these%20are%20examples%20of%20%26quot%3Bthings%20that%20would've%20never%20been%20able%20to%20happen%20before%20I%20started%20freelance%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBelow%20is%20the%20advice%20she%20would%20give%20parents%20and%20others%20who%20want%20to%20succeed%20as%20a%20freelancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBe%20professional%20and%20knowledgeable%20in%20the%20work%20you%20are%20offering%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20biggest%20advice%20to%20anybody%20is%20to%20become%20an%20expert%20in%20your%20craft%2C%20you%20have%20to%20provide%20good%20services%20in%20order%20to%20succeed%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20luck.%20You%20have%20to%20be%20a%20professional%20and%20provide%20quality%20work%20in%20order%20to%20succeed.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20from%20the%20start%2C%20she%20has%20used%20a%20professional%20photo%20on%20Fiverr%20and%20made%20sure%20to%20respond%20quickly%20while%20also%20doing%20%26quot%3Bexceptional%20work.%26quot%3B%20She%20credits%20this%20to%20her%20high%20return%20rate%20from%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20advised%20people%20looking%20to%20make%20a%20similar%20career%20chan