DP)%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20again%20Reddys%20(who%20occupy%20top%20positions%20in%20the%20Congress%20party)%20in%20Telangana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20in%20stark%20contrast%20to%20Kerala%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Karnataka%2C%20all%20of%20which%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsiddaramaiah-counter-modi-communal-obc-politics%5C%22%3Enow%20helmed%20by%20OBC%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20backward%20class%2C%20chief%20ministers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20devolution%20of%20power%20to%20more%20diverse%20sections%20of%20society%20in%20these%20three%20southern%20states%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%20the%20continued%20concentration%20of%20power%20within%20the%20wealthy%20castes%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Telangana%2C%20members%20of%20which%20have%20occupied%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20post%20for%20the%20past%20seven%20decades%2C%20barring%20minor%20exceptions%20(including%20in%20the%20undivided%20Andhra%20Pradesh).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaturally%2C%20there%20is%20no%20demand%20for%20a%20caste%20census%20in%20the%20Telugu%20states%20from%20the%20major%20parties.%20All%20the%20neighbouring%20chief%20ministers%20are%20now%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20(Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance)%20coalition%2C%20which%20has%20officially%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2F26-opposition-parties-joint-resolution-pitches-for-conducting-caste-census%2Farticle67094062.ece%5C%22%3Eadopted%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20caste%20census%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20exercise%20has%20been%20recognised%20as%20a%20necessity%20if%20there%20is%20ever%20to%20be%20a%20meaningful%20thrust%20towards%20an%20egalitarian%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fwhy-the-bjp-is-afraid-of-a-caste-census%5C%22%3EWhy%20the%20BJP%20is%20Afraid%20of%20a%20Caste%20Census%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%