20population%20increased%205.4%25%20to%20576%2C403%2C%20according%20to%20the%20latest%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.census.gov%2Fquickfacts%2Ffact%2Ftable%2Fwashingtoncountyarkansas%2Cmadisoncountyarkansas%2Cbentoncountyarkansas%2CUS%2FPST045222%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20Census%20Bureau%20data%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20about%20half%20the%20population%20of%20Austin%2C%20and%20about%20a%20seventh%20of%20the%20population%20of%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20and%20yet%20the%20grouping%20of%20counties%20is%20beginning%20to%20catch%20on%20among%20STEM%20workers%20who%20are%20looking%20for%20a%20different%20quality%20of%20life%2C%20like%20Falldine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ENorthwest%20Arkansas'%20plan%20to%20bring%20in%20new%20talent%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20like%20Walmart%2C%20Tyson%20Foods%2C%20and%20JB%20Hunt%20are%20headquartered%20in%20Northwest%20Arkansas%20and%20have%20been%20attracting%20movers%20for%20years.%20But%20the%20latest%20crop%20of%20movers%20are%20setting%20their%20roots%20for%20other%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBefore%20they%20were%20all%20coming%20in%20because%20they%20were%20corporate%2C%26quot%3B%20John%20Mayer%2C%20a%20real-estate%20agent%20with%20Better%20Homes%20and%20Gardens%20Real%20Estate%20Journey%20in%20Bentonville%2C%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BBut%20now%20Northwest%20Arkansas%20has%20become%20a%20destination%20for%20a%20better%20way%20of%20life.%20We're%20seeing%20people%20relocate%20because%20of%20the%20cost%2C%20the%20median%20price%20of%20housing%2C%20the%20low%20property%20taxes%2C%20and%20then%20all%20the%20great%20amenities%20we%20have%20for%20the%20outdoors.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20attract%20some%20of%20those%20movers%2C%20the%20Northwest%20Arkansas%20Council%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ea%20nonprofit%20economic%20development%20agency%2C%20rolled%20out%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-cities-pay-people-move-incentives-2018-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ean%20incentive%20to%20attract%20new%20residents%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20November%202020.%20The%20nonprofit%20offered%20%2410%2C000%20%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20mountain%20bike%20%E2%80%94%20to%20remote%20tech%20workers%20who%20moved%20to%20the%20region.%20One%20hundred%20people%20used%20the%20program%2C%20which%20ended%20in%20June%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20office%20space%20in%20Northwest%20Arkansas.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d63ac97e9149001aa4bb4c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221669%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Northwest%20Arkansas%20Council%20tried%20luring%20remote%20tech%20talent%20with%20%2410%2C000%20and%20a%20mountain%20bike.%3Cp%3ENWA%20Council%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENelson%20Peacock%2C%20the%20president%20and%20CEO%20of%20the%20Northwest%20Arkansas%20Council%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%20their%20plan%20was%20to%20attract%20%26quot%3BSTEAM%26quot%3B%20workers%20%E2%80%94%20an%20acronym%20for%20those%20in%20the%20science%2C%20technology%2C%20engineering%2C%20arts%2C%20and%20mathematics%20fields.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20a%20shortage%20of%20tech%20talent%20that%20we%20needed%20to%20address%2C%26quot%3B%20Peacock%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20knew%20that%20was%20the%20future%2C%20and%20we%20just%20knew%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20across%20the%20country%20didn't%20have%20a%20good%20awareness%20about%20what%20it%20was%20like%20to%20work%20and%20to%20live%20here.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EA%20millennial%20founder%20wanted%20more%20IRL%20networking%20opportunities%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EChris%20Thompson%20moved%20to%20Los%20Angeles%20from%20the%20Philadelphia%20area%20at%2024%20and%20started%20working%20in%20the%20fintech%20startup%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20thought%20that%20Los%20Angeles'%20fast-paced%20reputation%20would%20lead%20to%20more%20networking%2C%20but%20instead%20he%20took%20most%20of%20his%20meetings%20in%20front%20of%20a%20computer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20of%20a%20man%20posing%20in%20a%20park.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d6377e005c4a00183df325%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22630%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThompson%20moved%20from%20Los%20Angeles%20to%20Bentonville%2C%20Arkansas%2C%20for%20more%20in-person%20connections.%3Cp%3EChris%20Thompson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20all%20my%20meetings%20were%20over%20Zoom%2C%20even%20if%20they%20lived%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20because%20no%20one%20wants%20to%20get%20on%20the%20405%2C%26quot%3B%20Thompson%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BAll%20of%20the%20relationships%20that%20I%20had%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20most%20of%20them%20were%20not%20in-person%20relationships.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20working%20for%20a%20fintech%20startup%2C%20he%20noticed%20that%20around%20half%20of%20his%20team%20worked%20in%20Northwest%20Arkansas.%20He%20left%20the%20company%20and%20founded%20his%20own%20app%20in%202019%2C%20but%20stayed%20in%20contact%20with%20his%20former%20coworkers.%20With%20a%20built-in%20network%20of%20colleagues%20already%20in%20place%2C%20he%20joined%20them%20in%20Arkansas%20in%20June%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20before%20moving%20to%20Arkansas%2C%20Thompson%20founded%20Sober%20Sidekick%2C%20a%20healthcare%20app%20that%20helps%20users%20struggling%20with%20recovery%2C%20and%20prefers%20the%20relationships%20that%20he's%20forged%20in%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can%20build%20relationships%20here%20a%20lot%20faster%20than%20I%20could%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20of%20Walton's%20in%20Bentonville%2C%20Arkansas.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d66f031f51cc001967f507%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221753%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWalton's%2C%20the%20precursor%20of%20Walmart%2C%20started%20in%20Bentonville.%3Cp%3EKeith%20Myers%2FKansas%20City%20Star%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThompson%2C%20now%2029%2C%20took%20advantage%20of%20the%20%2410%2C000%20incentive%20program%2C%20which%20he%20said%20helped%20jumpstart%20his%20venture%20into%20homeownership.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20purchased%20a%202%2C000-square-foot%2C%20three-bedroom%20house%20in%20Bentonville%2C%20Arkansas%2C%20about%20two%20hours%20east%20of%20Tulsa%2C%20Oklahoma.%20His%20mortgage%20is%20%242%2C200%20a%20month%20%E2%80%94%20%24300%20cheaper%20than%20his%20previous%20rent%20for%20an%20800-square-foot%2C%20one-bedroom%20apartment%20in%20Marina%20Del%20Rey%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20sooner%20you%20can%20get%20into%20owning%2C%20the%20better%20off%20you're%20going%20to%20be%20in%20the%20long%20run%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20was%20a%20huge%20selling%20point%20for%20me.%20It's%20rent%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20for%20another%20five%20years%2C%20or%20start%20the%20process%20of%20building%20equity%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.realtor.com%2Frealestateandhomes-search%2FBentonville_AR%2Foverview%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emedian%20listing%20price%20in%20Bentonville%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20%24550%2C000%2C%20compared%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.realtor.com%2Frealestateandhomes-search%2FLos-Angeles_CA%2Foverview%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELos%20Angeles'%20%241.2%20million%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20according%20to%20realtor.com.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EA%20Texan%20looking%20for%20breathing%20room%20found%20some%20in%20Fayetteville%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFalldine%20only%20lived%20in%20Austin%20for%20about%20a%20year%2C%20but%20wasn't%20feeling%20the%20%26quot%3Bvibe.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20long%20car%20rides%20and%20general%20sense%20of%20overcrowding%20%E2%80%94%20both%20people%20and%20business%20establishments%20%E2%80%94%20led%20him%20and%20his%20family%20to%20Fayetteville.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20wanted%20to%20be%20close%20to%20family%2C%20and%20were%20looking%20for%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20same%20characteristics%20Austin%20has%3A%20aesthetically%20pleasing%2C%20quirky%2C%20creative%2C%20and%20unique%2C%26quot%3B%20Falldine%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20perk%20for%20Falldine%3A%20spontaneity%20in%20Fayetteville%20is%20more%20achievable.%20If%20it's%20a%20hot%20day%2C%20you%20can%20get%20in%20the%20car%20and%20go%20swimming%20near%20a%20waterfall%20with%20no%20hassle.%20In%20Austin%2C%20he%20said%20that%20the%20same%20experience%20would%20need%20to%20be%20booked%20weeks%20in%20advance%20because%20there%20were%20so%20many%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAustin's%20population%20of%20974%2C447%20far%20outnumbers%20Fayetteville's%2099%2C285%2C%20according%20to%202022%20estimates%20from%20the%20US%20Census%20Bureau%2C%20and%20that%20makes%20a%20big%20difference%20for%20Falldine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20colorful%20mural%20on%20the%20side%20of%20a%20building.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d639857e9149001aa4ba22%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221669%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20of%20the%20many%20murals%20in%20Northwest%20Arkansas.%3Cp%3ENWA%20Council%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFalldine%20likes%20the%20idea%20that%20Fayetteville%20is%20on%20its%20way%20up.%20When%20researching%20where%20to%20move%2C%20he%20was%20impressed%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fayetteville-ar.gov%2F1216%2FCity-Plan-2040%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C