0words%20for%20Elon%20Musk.%20Musk%2C%20for%20his%20part%2C%20has%20spent%20the%20weekend%20goading%20Zuckerberg%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-taunts-mark-zuckerberg-too-small-to-beat-him-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecomparing%20the%20differences%20in%20their%20physical%20sizes%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-goads-mark-zuckerberg-coward-chicken-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecalling%20the%20Meta%20CEO%20a%20chicken%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20martial%20arts%20community%20is%20small.%20Consensus%20from%20folks%20who%20have%20trained%20with%20either%20or%20both%20men%20is%20that%20Mark%20is%20way%20ahead%20of%20Elon%20in%20terms%20of%20technical%20abilities%2C%20fitness%2C%20training%20regimen%2C%20etc.%2C%26quot%3B%20Chatri%20told%20the%20SCMP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChatri%20said%20he%20would%20be%20willing%20for%20ONE%20Championship%20to%20host%20the%20fight%20night%2C%20but%20said%20his%20gut%20tells%20him%20that%20Musk%20is%20%26quot%3Bbluffing%26quot%3B%20about%20wanting%20to%20duke%20it%20out%20with%20Zuckerberg.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20he%20really%20wanted%20to%20fight%20Mark%2C%20he%20wouldn't%20be%20making%20up%20all%20these%20conditions%2C%20excuses%2C%20and%20stipulations%2C%26quot%3B%20Chatri%20said.%20%26quot%3BElon%20is%20doing%20bicep%20curls%20at%20the%20office%20while%20Mark%20is%20fighting%20people%20in%20his%20backyard%20cage.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZuckerberg%2C%20for%20one%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.threads.net%2F%40zuck%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0on%20Sunday%20that%20it's%20clear%20to%20him%20that%20Musk%20%26quot%3Bisn't%20serious%26quot%3B%20about%20a%20fight%20and%20that%20it's%20%26quot%3Btime%20to%20move%20on.%26quot%3B%20He%20added%20that%20he%20plans%20to%20%26quot%3Bfocus%20on%20competing%20with%20people%20who%20take%20the%20sport%20seriously%26quot%3B%20but%20is%20still%20game%20for%20a%20fight%20if%20Musk%20comes%20around%20and%20settles%20on%20a%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20for%20all%20of%20Musk's%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-bicep-curls-work-meeting-room-colleagues-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eflexing%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20tweeting%2C%20he%20hasn't%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-mri-neck-back-surgery-before-fight-mark-zuckerberg-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecommitted%20to%20a%20solid%20date%20for%20the%20fight.%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0On%20August%206%2C%20Musk%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1688377445957652480%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etweeted%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20he%20needed%20to%20get%20his%20neck%20and%20upper%20back%20scanned%20in%20an%20MRI.%20He%20then%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1689969006910861312%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etweeted%20on%20Friday%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20he%20now%20needs%20to%20get%20surgery%20for%20a%20shoulder%20injury.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk's%20representatives%20at%20Twitter%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Insider%20sent%20outside%20regular%20business%20hours.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fone-championship-ceo-says-musk-big-zuck-legit-fighter-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692006209000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64a627916075be0019c2c69c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fone-championship-ceo-says-musk-big-zuck-legit-fighter-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22ONE%20Championship%20CEO%20Chatri%20Sityodtong%20told%20the%20SCMP%20he%20thinks%20there's%20%26quot%3Ba%20wide%20disparity%20in%20skill%20level%20and%20fitness%20level%26quot%3B%20between%20Zuck%20and%20Musk.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Cheryl%20Teh)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A185%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fone-championship-ceo-says-musk-big-zuck-legit-fighter-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22These%20Are%20Most%20Liveable%20Cities%20In%20Asia-Pacific.%20How%20Do%20Indian%20Cities%20Rank%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20global%20city%2C%20Singapore%20is%20no%20stranger%20to%20being%20on%20%E2%80%9Cbest%E2%80%9D%20lists.%C2%A0%20Recent%20accolades%20it%20has%20picked%20up%20include%20the%20country%20with%20the%20%E2%80%9Cbest%20business%20environment%E2%80%9D%20(EIU)%2C%20%E2%80%9Cfreest%20economy%20in%20the%20world%E2%80%9D%20(The%20Heritage%20Foundation)%2C%20fourth%20most%20competitive%20economy%20in%20the%20world%20(International%20Institute%20for%20Management%20Development)%2C%20and%20eighth%20place%20in%20Schroders's%20global%20city%20index.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20it%20was%20with%20little%20surprise%20that%20it%20did%20not%20make%20it%20into%20the%20top%20ten%20cities%20in%20the%20latest%20Economist%20Intelligence%20Unit%20(EIU)%20ranking%20of%20the%20most%20liveable%20cities%20in%20the%20world.%20The%20Southeast%20Asian%20city%20did%20however%20sneak%20into%20the%20top%20among%20Asia-Pacific%20cities%20in%20tenth%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year's%20EIU%20liveability%20index%2C%20which%20provides%20a%20snapshot%20of%20the%20most%2C%20and%20least%2C%20desirable%20cities%20to%20live%20in%2C%20recorded%20the%20highest%20global%20average%20score%20in%2015%20years%2C%20showing%20that%20living%20conditions%20in%20cities%20across%20the%20world%20have%20fully%20recovered%20from%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20which%20disrupted%20lives%20and%20impacted%20lifestyles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20index%20rates%20living%20conditions%20in%20173%20cities%20across%20five%20categories%3A%20stability%2C%20healthcare%2C%20culture%20and%20environment%2C%20education%2C%20and%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20categories%20covered%20by%20the%20survey%2C%20only%20the%20stability%20score%20dropped%20on%20average%20in%202023.%20Although%20stability%20scores%20in%20many%20eastern%20European%20cities%2C%20which%20fell%20in%202022%20because%20they%20are%20close%20to%20Ukraine%2C%20rose%20this%20year%2C%20stability%20deteriorated%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStability%20scores%20were%20negatively%20affected%20by%20striking%20workers%20and%20protests%20in%20various%20European%20cities%20like%20Greece%20and%20France%20as%20well%20as%20deadly%20clashes%20in%20Israel%20and%20Peru.%20%C2%A0The%20EIU%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cinflation%20could%20lead%20to%20further%20falls%20in%20stability%20scores%2C%20and%20thus%20damage%20overall%20liveability%20scores%2C%20in%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20world%20over%20the%20next%20year.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20index%20revealed%20that%20cities%20in%20the%20Asia-Pacific%20region%20have%20rebounded%20the%20most%20with%20eight%20of%20the%20ten%20biggest%20upward%20movers%20coming%20from%20the%20region.%20New%20Zealand's%20Wellington%20rose%2035%20spots%20to%20take%2023rd%20place%2C%20while%20Auckland%20rose%2025%20places%20to%20land%20at%20number%2010.%20Hanoi%2C%20Vietnam%20moved%20up%2020%20places%20to%20129%2C%20whereas%20Kuala%20Lumpur%2C%20Malaysia%20jumped%2019%20positions.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPost-pandemic%20improvements%20in%20education%20and%20healthcare%20led%20to%20an%20improvement%20in%20scores%20across%20Asia.%20These%20two%20factors%20are%20also%20the%20main%20reason%20scores%20in%20Africa%20and%20the%20Middle%20East%20rose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EIU%20named%20Vienna%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9CCity%20of%20Music%E2%80%9D%2C%20also%20known%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9CCity%20of%20Dreams%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20most%20liveable%20city%20in%20the%20world%20for%20the%20fourth%20time%20in%20five%20years.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Economist%20report%20credited%20Vienna%20for%20its%20excellent%20mix%20of%20stability%2C%20culture%20and%20entertainment%2C%20and%20reliable%20infrastructure.%20Copenhagen%2C%20a%20similarly%20sized%20city%20with%20many%20of%20the%20same%20characteristics%2C%20is%20second.%20Melbourne%2C%20which%20regularly%20features%20among%20the%20top%20in%20the%20ranking%20came%20in%20third%20place.%20Fellow%20Aussie%20city%20Sydney%20is%20fourth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECanada%20has%20three%20cities%20in%20the%20top%20ten%20%E2%80%93%20Vancouver%20in%20fifth%2C%20Calgary%20in%207th%20and%20Toronto%20in%209th.%20The%20other%20cities%20that%20made%20it%20into%20the%20top%20ten%20are%20Zurich%20(6th)%2C%20Geneva%20(joint%207th)%2C%20Osaka%20(10th)%20and%20Auckland%20(joint%2010th).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20an%20expat%2C%20the%20downside%20of%20living%20in%20these%20cities%20is%20that%20you%20should%20not%20expect%20to%20receive%20any%20form%20of%20%E2%80%9Chardship%E2%80%9D%20compensation.%20The%20liveability%20survey%20was%20designed%20by%20the%20EIU%20to%20help%20companies%20calculate%20hardship%20allowances%20for%20staff%20who%20were%20moving%20to%20a%20new%20and%20possibly%20less%20tolerable%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20all%2C%20nine%20of%20the%20top%20ten%20cities%20are%20small%20to%20mid-sized.%20All%20ten%2C%20and%20indeed%20most%20of%20the%20top%2050%2C%20are%20in%20rich%20countries.%20Big%20cities%20with%20high%20levels%20of%20crime%2C%20congestion%20and%20density%20tend%20to%20fare%20less%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%2010%20cities%20to%20slip%20farthest%20down%20the%20rankings%2C%20three%20were%20in%20the%20UK%20%E2%80%94%20Edinburgh%2C%20Manchester%20and%20London%20%E2%80%94%20and%20two%20in%20the%20US%2C%20Los%20Angeles%20and%20San%20Diego.%20London%20fell%2012%20places%20from%20a%20year%20ago%20to%2046th%20and%20New%20York%20tumbled%20ten%20spots%20to%2069th.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20Chinese%20cities%20were%20%E2%80%9Cbroadly%20stable%20when%20compared%20to%20last%20year's%20results%2C%E2%80%9D%20according%20to%20the%20survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20four%20Indian%20cities%20in%20the%20study%2C%20New%20Delhi%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Chennai%20and%20Bangalore%2C%20are%20ranked%20between%20positions%2045%20and%2050%20among%20Asia-Pacific%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Asia-Pacific%20region%2C%20Karachi%2C%20Port%20Moresby%20(Papua%20New%20Guinea)%20and%20Dhaka%20are%20the%20three%20least%20desirable%20cities%20to%20live%20in.%20In%20the%20global%20rank%2C%20they%20are%20in%20positions%20169%2C%20168%2C%20and%20167%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20global%20table%2C%20Damascus%20took%20the%20dubious%20honour%20of%20the%20least%20liveable%20city%20in%20the%20world.%20It%20has%20held%20this%20place%20in%20the%20index%20for%20more%20than%20ten%20years.%20Tripoli%20is%20one%20space%20above%20in%20172%2C%20although%20its%20score%20is%20nearly%20ten%20points%20higher%20than%20that%20of%20Syria's%20war-ravaged%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKyiv%2C%20despite%20its%20efforts%20to%20protect%20itself%20from%20the%20war%2C%20also%20features%20in%20the%20bottom%20ten.%20It%20was%20excluded%20from%20the%20index%20in%202022%20because%20Russia%20invaded%20Ukraine%20while%20the%20data%20were%20being%20collected.%20Its%20infrastructure%20score%20of%2023.2%20out%20of%20100%20is%20the%20lowest%20in%20the%20index%2C%20thanks%20to%20Russian%20bombs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20shift%20towards%20normality%20after%20the%20pandemic%20has%20overall%20boded%20well%20for%20global%20liveability%20in%202023%2C%E2%80%9D%20Upasana%20Dutt%2C%20head%20of%20the%20liveability%20index%20at%20EIU%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%E2%80%9CEducat