don't%20put%20up%20appearances%20by%20sitting%20with%20another%20party's%20leaders%20as%20our%20workers%20fight.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Team%20Thackeray%20leader%20described%20Mr%20Pawar%20as%20the%20%26quot%3BBhishma%20Pitamaha%26quot%3B%20of%20Maharashtra%20politics%20and%20said%20he%20%26quot%3Bshould%20not%20do%20anything%20that%20creates%20doubt%20in%20the%20minds%20of%20people%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Raut%20said%20they%20had%20spoken%20to%20Maharashtra%20Congress%20chief%20Nana%20Patole%20over%20Mr%20Pawar's%20meeting%20with%20Ajit%20Pawar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Raut's%20remarks%20come%20after%20his%20party's%20mouthpiece%20Saamana%20said%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bamusing%26quot%3B%20to%20see%20Ajit%20Pawar%20frequently%20meeting%20Mr%20Pawar%20and%20the%20latter%20not%20avoiding%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20hunch%20that%20BJP's%20'Chanakya'%20is%20trying%20to%20create%20some%20confusion%20by%20sending%20Ajit%20to%20meet%20senior%20Pawar.%20However%2C%20such%20meetings%20tarnish%20the%20image%20of%20Sharad%20Pawar%20and%20it%20is%20not%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20veteran%20politician%20has%20asserted%20that%20his%20meeting%20with%20Ajit%20Pawar%20is%20a%20family%20meeting%20and%20that%20he%20has%20no%20plans%20to%20change%20camps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20media%20following%20a%20meeting%20with%20this%20nephew%2C%20Mr%20Pawar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAs%20the%20national%20president%20of%20the%20NCP%2C%20I%20am%20making%20it%20clear%20that%20my%20party%20(NCP)%20will%20not%20go%20with%20the%20BJP.%20Any%20association%20with%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20does%20not%20fit%20in%20NCP's%20political%20policy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20some%20%26quot%3Bwell-wishers%26quot%3B%20are%20trying%20to%20persuade%20him%20but%20he%20will%20never%20align%20with%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20flutter%20caused%20by%20the%20meeting%2C%20he%20said%