Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20stadium%20was%2095%25%20full.%20There%20were%20enough%20people%20there%20who%20could%20have%20intervened.%20Something%20like%20that%20is%20simply%20not%20appropriate%2C%20whether%20it%20happens%20in%20F%C3%BCrth%2C%20Nuremberg%20or%20Rostock%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20club%2C%20Green%20said%20it%20was%20one%20spectator%20during%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20let%20that%20upset%20us%20because%20I%20really%20wanted%20to%20win.%20And%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20hurts%20them%20the%20most%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHallescher%20spokeswomen%20Lisa%20Sch%C3%B6ppe%20apologised%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20club%20on%20Saturday%20for%20the%20misconduct%20of%20some%20spectators%20after%20Zorniger%E2%80%99s%20statements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fbayern-munich-condemn-racism-against-striker-mathys-tel%2Fa-66522717%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20originally%20published%20on%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%5C%22%3EDW%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692001026000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F14133655%2FMathys-Tel-in-2022.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Ffc-bayern-condemns-racist-abuse-of-striker-mathys-tel-at-super-cup-match%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20offensive%20comment%20was%20made%20on%20Instagram%20following%20the%20Bundesliga%20champion's%20defeat%20to%20RB%20Leipzig%20in%20the%20Super%20Cup%20on%20Saturday.%20A%20probe%20is%20underway%20after%20a%20separate%20racist%20incident%20at%20another%20match.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Ffc-bayern-condemns-racist-abuse-of-striker-mathys-tel-at-super-cup-match%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%2