1691952568295.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20families%20in%20a%20village%20in%20Uttarakhand%E2%80%99s%20Pauri%20Garwhal%20district%20have%20fled%20their%20homes%20as%20of%20Monday%20(August%2014)%20after%20more%20than%2050%20buildings%20developed%20cracks%20amid%20heavy%20rainfall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20organisation%20called%20the%20Joshimath%20Bachao%20Sangharsh%20Samiti%20has%20announced%20that%20it%20will%20protest%20the%20situation%20in%20Joshimath%20by%20holding%20a%20%3Cem%3Etiranga%20yatra%3C%2Fem%3E%20(tricolour%20march)%20on%20Independence%20Day%20(Tuesday%2C%20August%2015)%20and%20and%20hold%20sit-ins%20every%20day%20starting%20Wednesday%20(August%2016)%2C%20%3Cem%3EHT%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20reported%20that%20locals%20in%20Joshimath%20felt%20the%20government%20was%20being%20apathetic%20to%20the%20town%E2%80%99s%20current%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691998105000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F11122111%2F403207113_2fe454155f_c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fpeople-displaced-as-monsoon-sees-fresh-cracks-uttarakhand%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Joshimath%20Bachao%20Sangharsh%20Samiti%20has%20announced%20that%20it%20will%20hold%20a%20'tiranga'%20yatra%20on%20Indpendence%20Day%20and%20sit-ins%20every%20day%20from%20August%2016%20to%20protest%20the%20situation%20in%20the%20town.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fpeople-displaced-as-monsoon-sees-fresh-cracks-uttarakhand%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22New%20Post%20Office%20Bill%20Will%20Allow%20Employees%20to%20Open%2C%20Detain%20Parcels%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F10120705%2F144541-india-postpti.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20proposed%20revamp%20of%20the%20Indian%20Post%20Office%20Act%20will%20allow%20employees%20to%20open%20postal%20parcels%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20national%20security%20or%20public%20security%2C%20apart%20from%20also%20giving%20officers%20the%20power%20to%20divert%20them%20to%20the%20authorities%20concerned%20if%20there%20is%20suspicion%20of%20duty%20evasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fanother-colonial-era-law-indian-post-office-act-1898-to-be-repealed%2Farticle67187127.ece%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%20Businessline%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20these%20provisions%20are%20part%20of%20the%20Post%20Office%20Bill%2C%202023%20that%20was%20introduced%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20during%20the%20just-concluded%20monsoon%20session.%20It%20will%20repeal%20the%20Indian%20Post%20Office%20Act%2C%201898%20%E2%80%93%20a%20colonial-era%20law%20%E2%80%93%20and%20%E2%80%9Cconsolidate%20and%20amend%20the%20law%20relating%20to%20the%20Post%20Office%20in%20India%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20said%20that%20the%20Bill%20prescribes%20the%20power%20to%20%E2%80%9Cintercept%2C%20open%20or%20detain%20any%20item%20or%20deliver%E2%80%9D%20it%20to%20the%20customs%20authority.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Central%20Government%20may%2C%20by%20notification%2C%20empower%20any%20officer%20to%20cause%20any%20item%20in%20course%20of%20transmission%20by%20the%20Post%20Office%20to%20be%20intercepted%2C%20opened%20or%20detained%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20security%20of%20the%20State%2C%20friendly%20relations%20with%20foreign%20states%2C%20public%20order%2C%20emergency%2C%20or%20public%20safety%20or%20upon%20the%20occurrence%20of%20any%20contravention%20of%20any%20of%20the%20provisions%20of%20this%20Act%20or%20any%20other%20law%20for%20the%20time%20being%20in%20force%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20one%20provision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20postal%20officer%20will%20also%20be%20empowered%20to%20deliver%20an%20item%20that%20is%20received%20from%20a%20domestic%20or%20international%20source%20to%20customs%20or%20any%20concerned%20authority%20%E2%80%9Cin%20case%20there%20is%20suspicion%20of%20duty%20evasion%20or%20it%20is%20prohibited%20under%20the%20law%E2%80%9D.%20Those%20authorities%20will%20deal%20with%20such%20items%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20law%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EBusinessline%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20also%20a%20provision%20which%20says%20the%20Post%20Office%20and%20its%20officers%20%E2%80%9Cshall%20be%20exempt%20from%20any%20liability%20by%20reason%20of%20any%20loss%2C%20misdelivery%2C%20delay%20or%20damage%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20course%20of%20providing%20services.%20%E2%80%9CNo%20officer%20of%20the%20Post%20Office%20shall%20incur%20any%20liability%20with%20regard%20to%20a%20service%20provided%20by%20the%20Post%20Office%2C%20unless%20the%20officer%20has%20acted%20fraudulently%20or%20wilfully%20caused%20loss%2C%20delay%20or%20misdelivery%20of%20service%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Bill%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20person%20who%20avails%20a%20service%20provided%20by%20the%20Post%20Office%20shall%20be%20liable%20to%20pay%20the%20charges%20in%20respect%20of%20such%20service.%20If%20any%20person%20refuses%20or%20neglects%20to%20pay%20the%20charges%2C%20such%20amount%20shall%20be%20recoverable%20as%20if%20it%20were%20an%20arrear%20of%20land%20revenue%20due%20from%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20another%20provision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EBusinessline%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20Bill%20says%20post%20offices%20shall%20have%20exclusive%20privilege%20to%20issue%20postage%20stamps.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691997637000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F10120705%2F144541-india-postpti.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fnew-post-office-bill-employees-open-detain-parcels%2