which%20are%20in%20violation%20of%20social%20norms.%20It%20is%20necessary%20to%20bring%20amendments%20in%20the%20HMA%20to%20accommodate%20the%20conditions%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20social%20norms%20for%20maintaining%20the%20social%20fabric%20and%20a%20happy%20family%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kandela%20was%20quoted%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3ETribune%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDalal%20had%20also%20submitted%20a%20representation%20to%20the%20state%20government%20last%20month%20with%20the%20demand%20that%20in%20addition%20to%20intra-gotra%20and%20intra-village%20marriages%2C%20those%20between%20people%20from%20bordering%20villages%20should%20also%20be%20declared%20invalid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDalal%20said%20he%20was%20assured%20by%20top%20officials%20of%20the%20government%20that%20the%20matter%20had%20been%20assigned%20to%20a%20senior%20official%20who%20was%20likely%20to%20submit%20the%20final%20report%20to%20chief%20minister%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThereafter%2C%20the%20CM%20will%20take%20the%20final%20decision%20on%20the%20demand.%20In%20principle%2C%20the%20government%20was%20in%20agreement%20with%20me%20on%20the%20proposal%20for%20amendment%20in%20the%20HMA%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20was%20quoted%20by%20the%20paper%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20representation%20was%20submitted%20to%20the%20Haryana%20government%20on%20July%201%2C%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fchandigarh-news%2Fkhap-panchayats-in-haryana-demand-amendment-to-hindu-marriage-act-to-prohibit-same-gotra-marriages-101688410663798.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Nearly%20200%20%3Cem%3Emahapanchayats%3C%2Fem%3E%20have%20been%20organised%20by%20khap%20panchayats%20demanding%20the%20prohibition%20of%20such%20marriages%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691995982000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F14121527%2FF3T6TBIb0AAY7VK.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fharyana-govt-to-ban-intra-gotra-intra-village-marriages-as-per-khap-panchayats-demands%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%20government%20has%20begun%20the%20process%20of%20amending%20the%20Hindu%20Marriage%20Act%2C%201955.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A55%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fharyana-govt-to-ban-intra-gotra-intra-village-marriages-as-per-khap-panchayats-demands%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Elderly%20Citizens%20in%20India%20Are%20Finding%20Love%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F14085245%2FVillagers_from_india_16.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EMadhav%20Damle%20runs%20a%20home%20for%20senior%20citizens%20in%20Wai%2C%20a%20town%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Findia%2Ft-18996071%5C%22%3EIndia%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98s%20western%20state%20of%20Maharashtra.%20Years%20ago%2C%20his%20job%20made%20him%20face%20an%20uncomfortable%20truth%20%E2%80%94%20many%20of%20the%20residents%20were%20experiencing%20loneliness%20and%20stress%2C%20and%20had%20poor%20relations%20with%20their%20families%20and%20friends.%20At%20least%20one%20of%20the%20seniors%20under%20his%20care%20tried%20to%20commit%20suicide%20by%20consuming%20sleeping%20pills.%20His%20adult%20children%20expressed%20little%20interest%20in%20taking%C2%A0care%20of%20him%2C%20said%20Damle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20for%20ways%20to%20ease%20his%20clients%E2%80%99%20isolation%2C%20Damle%20had%20an%20idea%20%E2%80%94%20he%20tried%20matching%20them%20into%20couples%20with%20a%20perspective%20of%20marriage.%20This%20worked%20especially%20well%20for%20clients%20in%20their%20mid%20to%20late%2060s.%20But%20he%20then%20faced%20an%20unexpected%20obstacle%2C%20as%20some%20of%20the%20clients%E2%80%99%20children%20disliked%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Findia-elderly-couple-sue-son-over-lack-of-grandchildren%2Fa-61768426%5C%22%3Eelderly%20relatives%3C%2Fa%3E%20marrying%2C%20due%20to%20inheritance%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20why%2C%20I%20thought%20live-in%20relationships%20might%20be%20a%20good%20solution%20for%20the%20couples.%20We%20conducted%20a%20survey%20among%20some%20seniors%20in%20%5Bthe%20Maharashtra%20city%20of%5D%20Pune%2C%20and%20about%2070%25%20of%20them%20were%20open%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20live-in%20partner%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Time%20and%20love%E2%80%99%20as%20top%20priorities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20society%20is%20remarkably%20conservative%20when%20it%C2%A0comes%20to%20marriage%20and%20relationships.%20The%20divorce%20rate%20in%20India%20is%20about%201%25%20%E2%80%94%20among%20the%20lowest%20in%20the%20world.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20there%20is%20a%20social%20stigma%20against%20remarrying%20and%20against%20unmarried%20couples%20living%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20has%20even%20made%20it%20to%20the%20Indian%20Supreme%20Court%20in%202006%2C%20with%20the%20judges%20finding%20that%20a%20%E2%80%9Clive-in%20relationship%20between%20two%20consenting%20adults%20of%20heterogenic%20sex%20does%20not%20amount%20to%20any%20offense%2C%20even%20though%20it%20may%20be%20perceived%20as%20immoral.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDamle%20officially%20started%20his%20matchmaking%20agency%20in%202012%2C%20which%20later%20came%20to%20be%20known%20as%20%E2%80%9CHappy%20Seniors.%E2%80%9D%20He%20is%20managing%20and%20sharing%20profiles%2C%20while%20also%20organizing%20meet-ups%20and%20trips%20for%20his%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitin%20Savgave%20and%20Saroj%20Ghatani%20found%20each%20other%20through%20Damle.%20The%20two%20are%20now%20married.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20only%20requirement%20from%20a%20partner%20was%20their%20time%20and%20love.%20I%20got%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ghatani%20told%20DW.%20She%20added%20that%20her%20family%20did%20not%20approve%20of%20her%20new%20marriage%2C%20but%20this%20did%20not%20deter%20her%20and%C2%A0Savgave.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20enjoy%20each%20others%E2%80%99%20company%20and%20spend%20most%20of%20our%20time%20together%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0Ghatani%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESavgave%E2%80%99s%20family%20was%20more%20supportive.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20is%20vegetarian%2C%20whereas%20I%20eat%20meat%20frequently%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20we%20have%20adapted%20to%20each%20other%20and%20enjoy%20the%20companionship.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMinefield%20of%20dating%20apps%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Findianmatchmakingfraught-with-sexism-class-and-caste-issues%2Fa-55174165%5C%22%3EMatchmaking%20is%20a%20time-honored%20craft%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20India.%20But%20finding%20a%20partner%20online%20is%20growing%20increasingly%20common%2C%20and%20even%20some%20older%20Indians%20are%20turning%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fhow-indians-with-disabilities-find-love-through-dating-apps%2Fa-64784892%5C%22%3Emodern%20dating%20apps%20to%20find%20love%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETina%20(name%20changed)%2C%2064%2C%20decided%20to%20do%20just%20that%20after%20walking%20out%20of%20an%20abusive%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20got%20married%20at%2018%20and%20became%20a%20mum%20by%2020%2C%20I%20never%20got%20the%20chance%20to%20be%20myself.%C2%A0%20So%20after%20I%20split%2C%20I%20had%20all%20this%20freedom%20and%20no%20one%20to%20dictate%20my%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%20DW.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20while%2C%20she%20tried%20using%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fonline-dating%2Ft-38790642%5C%22%3Edating%20apps%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20search%20of%20companionship.%20%E2%80%9CI%20found%20a%20lot%20of%20men%20were%20married%2C%20and%20looking%20to%20cheat%20on%20their%20wives.%20There%20were%20also%20some%20younger%20men%20looking%20for%20an%20older%20woman.%20I%20got%20fed%20up%20with%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20admitted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20her%20frustration%20eventually%20paid%20off.%20She%20found%20a%20partner%20through%20an%20app%2C%20and%20%E2%80%94%20after%20chatting%20for%20about%20five%20years%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0%20the%20two%20finally%20met.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99re%20both%20definitely%20not%20looking%20for%20marriage.%20Just%20companionship%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20children%20know%20about%20her%20relationship.%20Her%20partner%20also%20has%20one%20child%20and%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20acceptance%20has%20not%20been%20forthcoming%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tina%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMost%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20seniors%20lonely%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20breaking%20taboos%20is%20likely%20to%20grow%20increasingly%20common%20as%20both%20India%E2%80%99s%20society%20and%20its%20population%20shift.%20Today%2C%20about%205.7%25%20of%20Indian%20senior%20citizens%20live%20alone%20without%20the%20support%20of%20family%20or%20friends%2C%20according%20to%20a%20survey%20by%20India%E2%80%99s%20PAN%20Healthcare.%20It%20was%20conducted%20among%2010%2C000%20elderly%20population%20across%2010%20cities%20in%20India%2C%20and%20also%20found%20that%20a%20majority%20of%20responders%20feel%20lonely%20at%20least%20some%20of%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20with%20India%20now%20the%20most%20populous%20country%20in%20the%20word%2C%20the%20number%20of%20its%20seniors%20is%20climbing%20%E2%80%94%20the%20UN%20Population%20Fund%20said%20it%20will%20touch%20192%20million%20by%202030%2C%20and%2C%20by%202050%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fdemographics%2Ft-62940381%5C%22%3Eevery%20fifth%20Indian%20will%20be%20an%20elderly%20person%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20defined%20by%20the%20UN%20as%20aged%2060%20or%20older.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fhow-elderly-citizens-in-india-are-finding-love%2Fa-66504452%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20originally%20published%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%5C%22%3EDW%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691995559000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F14085245%2FVillagers_from_india_16.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fhow-elderly-citizens-in-india-are-finding-love%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22More%20and%20more%20Indian%20seniors%20are%20refusing%20to%20spend%20their%20twilight%20years%20alone%20and%20are%20turning%20to%20matchmaking%20and%20dating%20apps.%20But%20this%20means%20breaking%20some%20deep-seated%20taboos.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fhow-elderly-citizens-in-india-are-finding-love%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Accurately%20Do%20We%20Measure%20Poverty%20in%20India%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F14120533%2F4882154176_e9f0324cee_c.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EA%20significant%20decline%20in%20poverty%20%E2%80%93%20this%20is%20what%20a%20recent%20NITI%20Aayog%20report%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20published%20showed%20that%20over%20a%20span%20of%20five%20years%2C%20about%2013.5%20crore%20Indians%20came%20out%20of%20poverty.%20In%20fact%2C%20this%20measure%20was%20of%20multidimensional%20poverty%2C%20therefore%20it%20seemed%20that%20on%20the%20whole%2C%20crores%20of%20people%20enjoyed%20the%20fruits%20of%20holistic%20progress.%20They%20are%20no%20longer%20below%20the%20poverty%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20does%20the%20methodology%20and%20its%20results%20hold%20up%20to%20closer%20examination%3F%20Has%20the%20%E2%80%98multidimensional%E2%80%99%20index%20been%20able%20to%20capture%20the%20full%20picture%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20not.%20To%20start%20with%2C%20the%20government%20of%20India%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20tell%20citizens%20the%20number%20and%20share%20of%20the%20population%20below%20the%20consumption%20poverty%20line%2C%20which%20has%20been%20the%20traditional%20method%20of%20estimating%20poverty%20globally%20for%20decades.%20India%20has%20used%20consumption%20poverty%20as%20the%20measure%20for%20over%20four%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20had%20not%20released%20a%20consumption%20expenditure%20survey%20conducted%20by%20the%20National%20Survey%20Organisation%20(NSO)%20in%202017-18.%20The%20NSO%20has%20announced%20consumption%20expenditure%20surveys%20for%202022-23%20and%202023-24.%20These%20might%20reveal%20to%20us%20what%20has%20happened%20to%20consumption%20(or%20money-metric)%20poverty%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20NITI%20Aayog%20has%20just%20released%20the%20national%20multidimensional%20poverty%20index%20(MPI)%20for%20India%2C%20a%20few%20days%20after%20the%20global%20MPI%20estimates%20were%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2010%20indicators%20of%20the%20global%20MPI%20are%20a%20mishmash%20of%20very%20different%20types%20of%20indicators.%20Some%20are%20indicators%20of%20inputs%2C%20others%20of%20process%2C%20yet%20others%20are%20output%20or%20outcome%20indicators.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20education%20ones%20%E2%80%93%20having%20not%20completed%206%20years%20of%20school%20and%20children%20up%20to%20Class%208%20not%20attending%20school%20%E2%80%93%20are%20output%20and%20process%20indicators%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20health%20ones%20are%20both%20outcome%20indicators%20%E2%80%93%20adult%20body%20mass%20index%20and%20child%20nutrition.%20All%20six%20indicators%20of%20standard%20of%20living%20are%20input-based%20%E2%80%93%20electricity%2C%20drinking%20water%2C%20sanitation%2C%20cooking%20fuel%2C%20home%20floor%20and%20consumer%20assets.%20In%20statistics%2C%20it%20is%20theoretically%20flawed%20to%20lump%20together%20such%20different%20indicators%20to%20construct%20an%20index.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENational%20and%20global%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20this%2C%20the%20national%20MPI%20(NMPI)%20indicator%20framework%20has%20been%20modified%20vis-%C3%A0-vis%20global%20MPI%20and%20interestingly%2C%20no%20reason%20has%20been%20provided%20in%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NMPI%20framework%20has%2012%20instead%20of%2010%20globally%20considered%20indicators.%20The%20two%20new%20indicators%20are%3A%20Maternal%20health%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98health%E2%80%99%20dimension%20and%20access%20to%20banking%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98standards%20of%20living%E2%80%99%20dimension.%20This%20addition%20leads%20to%20change%20in%20the%20weights%20assigned%20to%20the%20two%20indicators%2C%20which%20were%20the%20two%20high-contributing%20factors%20to%20poverty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20global%20MPI%202022%20report%2C%20released%20a%20few%20weeks%20ago%2C%20had%20reported%20that%20India%20had%20reduced%20its%20incidence%20of%20multidimensional%20poverty%20from%2054%25%20in%202005-06%20(National%20Family%20Health%20Survey%203)%20to%2027.9%25%20of%20the%20total%20population%20in%202015-16%20(NFHS%204)%2C%20halving%20the%20head%20count%20ratio.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECompared%20to%20that%2C%20the%20global%20MPI%20reported%20that%20the%20reduction%20in%20multidimensional%20poverty%20between%202015-16%20was%20from%2027.9%25%20to%2016%25%20in%202019-21%20(NFHS%205).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fks-james-nfhs-modi-government-data-sets-iips%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Unhappy%20With%20Data%20Sets%2C%E2%80%99%20Modi%20Govt%20Suspends%20Director%20of%20Institute%20Which%20Prepares%20NFHS%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EExcluding%20millions%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20the%20global%20nutrition%20indicator%20was%20modified%20in%20NMPI%2C%20leaving%20out%20children%20aged%20six%20to%2014%20years%2C%20consisting%20of%20more%20than%2018%25%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20population.%20More%20than%20two-third%20of%20this%20population%20group%20suffers%20from%20anemia.%20NMPI%20thus%20leaves%20many%20poor%20and%20deprived%20out%20of%20the%20count%20on%20this%20account.%20More%20importantly%2C%20the%20NMPI%20uses%20undernourishment%20of%20under-fives%20(weight%20for%20age)%2C%20while%20the%20global%20MPI%20uses%20a%20more%20robust%20indicator%20%E2%80%93%20stunting%20(height%20for%20age).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latter%20is%20higher%20(35.5%25%20in%20NFHS%205)%20in%20India%20than%20the%20underweight%20measure%20(31.1%25%20in%20NFHS%205).%20Worse%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20stunting%20rate%20is%20higher%20than%20that%20of%20Sub-saharan%20Africa%20(32%25)%3B%20just%20as%20India%E2%80%99s%20child%20wasting%20rate%20is%2019.1%25%20(NFHS%205)%2C%20while%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20is%206%25%20(UNICEF%2C%202023%2C%20State%20of%20World%E2%80%99s%20Children).%20Moreover%2C%20the%20recently%20released%20%E2%80%98The%20State%20of%20Food%20Security%20and%20Nutrition%20in%20the%20World%202023%E2%80%99%20report%20by%20the%20UN%20highlighted%20that%20104.3%20crore%20(74.1%25)%20Indians%20are%20unable%20to%20afford%20healthy%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecondly%2C%20selection%20of%20the%20new%20indicator%20on%20maternal%20health%20is%20faulty.%20It%20regards%20a%20pregnant%20woman%20to%20be%20deprived%20if%20her%20delivery%20is%20executed%20by%20an%20unskilled%20health%20personnel%20or%20if%20she%20has%20not%20availed%20the%20prescribed%20four%20antenatal%20care%20services.%20Most%20deliveries%20(more%20than%2080%25)%20are%20now%20happening%20in%20a%20health%20institution.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20there%20are%20very%20few%20deprived%20on%20this%20indicator.%20This%20will%20tend%20to%20significantly%20reduce%20the%20count%20of%20deprived%20pregnant%20women%2C%20reducing%20the%20overall%20number%20of%20persons%20falling%20under%20the%20category%20of%20multidimensionally%20poor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThirdly%2C%20take%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20addition%20of%20a%20new%20indicator%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%98No%20household%20member%20has%20a%20bank%20account%20or%20a%20post%20office%20account%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20standard%20of%20living%20dimension.%20As%20per%20NFHS%204%2C%20nine%20out%20of%2010%20persons%20in%20the%20country%20(90.3%25)%20had%20either%20a%20bank%20account%20and%2For%20a%20post%20office%20account.%20While%20this%20is%20a%20major%20achievement%20for%20computation%20of%20deprivation%20and%20policy%20purposes%2C%20inclusion%20of%20this%20indicator%20significantly%20influences%20the%20overall%20number%20of%20deprived%20persons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDiffering%20data%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20and%20most%20worrying%20is%20the%20following%3A%20The%20MPI%20estimate%20for%20multidimensionally%20poor%20people%20in%20India%20in%202019-21%20estimates%20reduction%20from%20the%202015-16%20figure.%20The%20NITI%20Aayog%E2%80%99s%20report%20estimates%20the%20number%20of%20people%20rising%20out%20of%20poverty%20to%20be%20135%20million.%20However%2C%20there%20is%20a%20sleight%20of%20hand%20in%20the%20NITI%20Aayog%20estimate.%20I%20double%20checked%20the%20projected%20population%20used%20for%202015-16%20and%20for%202019-21%20as%20a%20denominator%20for%20determining%20the%20absolute%20number%20of%20MPI%20poor%20in%20each%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EObviously%2C%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20exact%20population%20data%20between%20census%20years%2C%20we%20use%20population%20projections%2C%20as%20provided%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Health%20and%20Family%20Welfare%2C%20based%20on%20Census%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaturally%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20projected%20population%20in%202021%20will%20be%20higher%20than%20that%20in%202015-16.%20To%20arrive%20at%20the%20number%20of%20MPI%20poor%20for%202021%2C%20that%20year%E2%80%99s%20population%20should%20be%20used%3B%20and%20to%20arrive%20at%20the%20number%20of%20MPI%20poor%20for%202015-16%2C%20again%20the%20latter%20year%E2%80%99s%20population%20should%20be%20used.%20If%2C%20on%20the%20one%20hand%2C%C2%A0%20someone%20uses%20the%20same%20estimate%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20total%20population%20for%20both%20years%2C%20the%20number%20of%20people%20pulled%20out%20of%20MPI%20poverty%20will%20be%20overstated.%20That%20is%20exactly%20what%20I%20found%20the%20NITI%20Aayog%20has%20done.%20The%20estimated%20population%20for%20both%20years%20was%20found%20to%20be%20the%20same.%20The%20result%20is%20that%20the%20NITI%20Aayog%20is%20claiming%20that%20India%20pulled%20135%20million%20out%20of%20MPI%20poverty%2C%20when%20in%20fact%20that%20number%20is%20really%20around%20118%20million%20(because%20the%20total%20population%20of%20India%20in%202015%20was%20naturally%20lower%20than%20in%202021).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20even%20if%20one%20goes%20by%20the%20NMPI%20estimates%20for%202019-21%20and%20projects%20it%20onto%20the%202021%20estimated%20population%2C%20410%20million%20people%20are%20still%20deprived%20on%20the%20sanitation%20indicator%20of%20NMPI.%20Yet%2C%20the%20government%20has%20claimed%20that%20India%20has%20become%20open%20defecation%20free.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20unfortunate%20that%20government%20estimates%20fail%20to%20paint%20an%20accurate%20picture%20of%20the%20realities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESantosh%20Mehrotra%20was%20the%20chief%20economist%20of%20the%20global%20Human%20Development%20Report%20(2002-04)%2C%20UNDP%20New%20York%2C%20and%20the%20lead%20author%20of%20the%20second%20India%20Human%20Development%20Report%20(OUP%2C%202011)%20of%20the%20Planning%20Commission%20of%20India.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20first%20appeared%20on%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fhow-are-we-defining-and-measuring-poverty-in-india-2645724%5C%22%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20and%20has%20been%20republished%20with%20permission.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691995290000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F14120533%2F4882154176_e9f0324cee_c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fpoverty-measure-niti-aayog-decline%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Has%20the%20%E2%80%98multidimensional%E2%80%99%20index%20been%20able%20to%20capture%20the%20full%20picture%3F%C2%A0Unfortunately%20not.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fpoverty-measure-niti-aayog-decline%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22July%20WPI-based%20inflation%20comes%20at%20-1.36%25%20as%20food%20prices%20skyrocket%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691995225000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2020-08%2F14%2Ffull%2F1597345167-5331.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fjuly-wpi-based-inflation-comes-at-1-36-as-food-prices-skyrockets-123081400237_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22WPI%20inflation%20in%20primary%20articles%20was%20considerably%20higher%20at%207.57%20per%20cent%20as%20compared%20to%20July%20last%20year%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fjuly-wpi-based-inflation-comes-at-1-36-as-food-prices-skyrockets-123081400237_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fjuly-wpi-based-inflation-comes-at-1-36-as-food-prices-skyrockets-123081400237_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fjuly-wpi-based-inflation-comes-at-1-36-as-food-prices-skyrockets-123081400237_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rajinikanth%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Jailer%2C%E2%80%99%20Sunny%20Deol%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Gadar%202%2C%E2%80%99%20Chiranjeevi%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Bhola%20Shankar%2C%E2%80%99%20Akshay%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20OMG%202%E2%80%B2%20Create%20Indian%20Box%20Office%20History%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691993842000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FJailer-Gadar-2-Bhola-Shankar.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235695378%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20combined%20performances%20of%20Rajinikanth%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9CJailer%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sunny%20Deol%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9CGadar%202%2C%E2%80%9D%20Akshay%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9COMG%202%E2%80%9D%20and%20Chiranjeevi%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9CBhola%20Shankar%E2%80%9D%20have%20set%20a%20new%20all-time%C2%A0theatrical%20gross%20box%20office%20record%20for%20the%20Indian%20cinema%20industry.%20Numbers%20released%20by%20the%20Multiplex%20Association%20of%20India%20and%20the%20Producers%20Guild%20of%20India%20reveal%20that%20the%20Aug.%2011-13%20weekend%20was%20the%20busiest%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Naman%20Ramachandran%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fasia%2Frajinikanth-jailer-sunny-deol-gadar-2-chiranjeevi-bhola-shankar-india-box-office-1235695378%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fasia%2Frajinikanth-jailer-sunny-deol-gadar-2-chiranjeevi-bhola-shankar-india-box-office-1235695378%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fasia%2Frajinikanth-jailer-sunny-deol-gadar-2-chiranjeevi-bhola-shankar-india-box-office-1235695378%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98They%20Had%20No%20Idea%20How%20Gay%20People%20Exist%E2%80%99%3A%20Queer%20Comedian%20Breaks%20Barriers%20in%20Comedy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENavin%20Noronha%2C%20a%2031-year-old%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F153761%2Fdeepika-mhatre-mumbai-domestic-help-stand-up-comedian%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estand-up%20comic%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20podcaster%20from%20Mumbai%2C%20was%2014%20when%20he%20knew%20he%20was%20queer%20(gay).%20But%20he%20was%20also%20raised%20as%20a%20staunch%20Catholic.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20tried%20to%20first%20do%20away%20with%20that%20%5Bfeeling%20attracted%20to%20boys%5D%20by%20joining%20Bible%20camps.%20When%20I%20was%20in%20Class%208%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20priests%20coming%20to%20our%20church%20recognised%20me%20as%20a%20very%20talented%20and%20outspoken%20child.%20At%20a%20very%20young%20age%2C%20I%20was%20groomed%20to%20become%20a%20Catholic%20priest.%20But%20that%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20realised%20I%20like%20men%20and%20that%20duality%20set%20in.%20So%2C%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20say%20anything%20about%20it%20for%20a%20very%20long%20time%20until%20I%20was%2019%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Navin%2C%20speaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENavin%20first%20came%20out%20to%20his%20best%20friend%20Amit%2C%20who%20he%20knew%20since%20they%20were%2010.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20already%20knew%20each%20other%20very%20well%2C%20although%20we%20were%20never%20friends%20who%20spoke%20about%20personal%20stuff.%20So%2C%20when%20I%20came%20out%20to%20him%2C%20it%20was%20only%20a%20matter%20of%20fact.%20I%20just%20kind%20of%20came%20out%20to%20him%20and%20nothing%20changed%20after%20that%20because%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20being%20gay%20is%20really.%20People%20who%20know%20you%2C%20know%20you%20for%20who%20you%20are.%20What%20gender%20you%20sleep%20with%20barely%20makes%20a%20difference%20to%20them%20in%20the%20long%20run%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20he%20was%2021%20and%20in%20his%20third%20year%20of%20college%2C%20he%20had%20come%20out%20to%20most%20of%20his%20friends.%20He%20says%20he%20felt%20the%20need%20to%20tell%20all%20his%20friends%20and%20acquaintances%20that%20he%20was%20gay%20because%20he%20had%20begun%20feeling%20left%20out%20from%20their%20conversations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20also%20wanted%20to%20chime%20in%2C%20but%20that%E2%80%99s%20when%20people%20would%20share%20weird%20notions%20of%20what%20gay%20people%20are%20with%20me.%20Listening%20to%20them%2C%20I%20found%20some%20of%20their%20notions%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F152754%2Fiit-madras-kaushik-section-377-supreme-court%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egay%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20be%20hilarious.%20They%20had%20no%20idea%20about%20gay%20people%20and%20how%20we%20exist.%20That%20became%20the%20subject%20of%20my%20first%20comedy%20set%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FNavin-Noronha-01-1691803028.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Queer%20Comedian%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FNavin-Noronha-01-1691803028.jpg%201365w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FNavin-Noronha-01-1691803028-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FNavin-Noronha-01-1691803028-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FNavin-Noronha-01-1691803028-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FNavin-Noronha-01-1691803028-768x768.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FNavin-Noronha-01-1691803028-96x96.jpg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-327138%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENavin%20Noronha%20is%20giving%20a%20platform%20to%20other%20queer%20comedians.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EQueer%20comics%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Navin%20was%2023%2C%20he%20started%20doing%20stand-up%20comedy%20seriously.%20During%20these%20open%20mics%2C%20he%E2%80%99d%20take%20all%20these%20notions%20that%20his%20friends%20had%20of%20gay%20people%2C%20and%20turn%20them%20into%20jokes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20he%20came%20out%20to%20his%20friend%2012%20years%20ago%20%E2%80%94%20and%20began%20performing%20as%20a%20full-time%20comic%20eight%20years%20ago%20%E2%80%94%20a%20lot%20has%20changed.%20After%20years%20of%20touring%2C%20he%20released%20his%20first%20special%20%E2%80%98The%20Good%20Child%E2%80%99%20on%20YouTube%20in%20late%20June%202023.%20In%20the%20meantime%2C%20Navin%20has%20not%20only%20spread%20laughter%2C%20but%20also%20curated%20a%20lineup%20of%20LGBTQ%2B%20performers.%20They%20went%20on%20tour%20to%20Delhi%20in%20June%20and%20Mumbai%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBefore%20the%20pandemic%2C%20there%20were%20only%20a%20couple%20of%20us%20comics%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Ayushi%20Jagad%2C%20Manvendra%20Singh%2C%20Ankur%20Tangde%20and%20I%20%E2%80%94%20who%20were%20openly%20talking%20about%20our%20queer%20lives.%20Today%2C%20we%20have%20about%2020%20comics%20who%20are%20out%20and%20proud.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20done%20sold%20out%20shows%20in%20Delhi%20and%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20are%20looking%20to%20do%20the%20same%20in%20Bengaluru%20and%20Kolkata%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Navin.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20says%20that%20it%20takes%20grit%2C%20money%2C%20and%20resources%20to%20set%20up%20these%20shows.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20queer%20comics%2C%20we%20want%20to%20create%20spaces%20where%20other%20queer%20people%20can%20just%20vibe%2C%20thrive%20and%20nobody%20can%20tell%20us%20anything.%20I%20live%20for%20that.%20What%20we%20have%20done%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years%20is%20try%20our%20best%20to%20make%20this%20a%20safer%20space%20for%20the%20coming%20generations.%20Today%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20venues%20are%20pro-queer%20rights%20like%20Depot%2048%20in%20Delhi.%20Another%20example%20is%20the%20Social%20chain%20of%20cafes%2C%20which%20has%20been%20so%20proactive.%20They%20host%20the%20Queer%20Comedy%20Mic%20for%20us%20too.%20These%20are%20small%20steps%2C%20but%20we%E2%80%99re%20doing%20what%20we%20can%20joyfully%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20Navin%20utilises%20his%20public%20speaking%20engagements%20to%20address%20corporate%20and%20educational%20spaces%2C%20fostering%20understanding%20and%20inclusivity%20for%20queer%20individuals%20in%20professional%20and%20academic%20environments.%20His%20impact%20extends%20far%20beyond%20the%20Indian%20comedy%20circuit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FSnapinsta.app_169502534_271463471131437_1152995525555498624_n_1080-1691803119.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Queer%20Comedian%20from%20Mumbai%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FSnapinsta.app_169502534_271463471131437_1152995525555498624_n_1080-1691803119.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FSnapinsta.app_169502534_271463471131437_1152995525555498624_n_1080-1691803119-300x159.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FSnapinsta.app_169502534_271463471131437_1152995525555498624_n_1080-1691803119-500x264.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FSnapinsta.app_169502534_271463471131437_1152995525555498624_n_1080-1691803119-768x406.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FSnapinsta.app_169502534_271463471131437_1152995525555498624_n_1080-1691803119-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-327140%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22571%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98The%20more%20I%20delved%20into%20my%20queer%20self%2C%20the%20more%20I%20realised%20that%20this%20is%20my%20reality%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20out%2C%20Navin%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20really%20fearful%20of%20talking%20about%20his%20sexuality%2C%20and%20credits%20some%20of%20his%20%E2%80%98seniors%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20business%20for%20giving%20out%20useful%20pointers.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20senior%20comics%20%E2%80%94%20Kunal%20Kamra%20and%20Sapan%20Verma%20for%20me%20%E2%80%94%20would%20advise%20us%20that%20%E2%80%98Maybe%20perfect%20that%20one%20five-minute%20set%E2%80%99.%20In%20the%20open%20mic%20circuit%2C%20there%20are%20so%20many%20of%20us%20performing%20at%20the%20same%20time%20that%20you%20also%20have%20to%20stand%20out.%20I%20knew%20that%20being%20queer%20on%20a%20given%20lineup%20was%20definitely%20going%20to%20be%20a%20standout%20because%20nobody%20%5Bin%20the%20audience%5D%20knew%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20five-minute%20set%20Navin%20tried%20to%20perfect%20was%20about%20his%20coming%20out%20experiences.%20However%2C%20his%20set%20was%20initially%20not%20doing%20well.%20Paying%20Rs%20300%20to%20just%20travel%20from%20North%20Bombay%20to%20South%20Bombay%20and%20an%20additional%20Rs%20300%20to%20perform%20an%20open%20mic%20set%20at%20the%20Canvas%20Laugh%20Club%20initially%20didn%E2%80%99t%20seem%20like%20a%20worthwhile%20pursuit.%20Naturally%2C%20some%20doubts%20had%20begun%20to%20creep%20in.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAllaying%20my%20doubts%2C%20comics%20like%20Sapan%20and%20Kaneez%20(Surka)%20were%20kind%20enough%20to%20say%2C%20%E2%80%98Maybe%20break%20it%20%5Bbeing%20gay%5D%20down%20for%20straight%20people%E2%80%99%3B%20%E2%80%98Maybe%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20the%20concept%20of%20top%20and%20bottom%20means%E2%80%99%3B%20or%20%E2%80%98They%20%5Bstraight%20people%5D%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20Grindr%20is.%20They%20%5Bstraight%20people%5D%20have%20no%20idea%20about%20queer%20people%20in%20this%20country%20and%20how%20they%20live%2C%20right%3F%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20pointers%20made%20sense.%20My%20first%20idea%20was%20that%20the%205-minute%20set%20has%20to%20become%20a%2010-minute%20one%20because%20I%E2%80%99m%20going%20to%20break%20everything%20down%20slowly%2C%20and%20therein%20the%20humour%20came%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20recent%20special%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20see%20Navin%20explaining%20top%20and%20bottom%20%5Bsex%20positions%5D%20to%20people.%20These%20jokes%20are%20the%20outcome%20of%20trialling%20them%20for%20years%20before%20implementing%20them%20in%20real%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20when%20I%20say%20jokes%20like%2C%20%E2%80%98Kerala%20is%20bottom%2C%20Delhi%20is%20top%E2%80%99%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20call%20back%20to%20the%20audience%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20also%20an%20inbuilt%20joke%20as%20well.%20The%20demographic%20of%20the%20country%20also%20is%20very%20vivid%20in%20terms%20of%20sexual%20preferences.%20The%20%E2%80%98top%20and%20bottom%E2%80%99%20joke%20has%20become%20a%20reel%20on%20my%20Instagram%20handle.%20If%20you%20read%20the%20comments%20section%20right%20now%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20full%20of%20gay%20people%20trying%20to%20hook%20up%20with%20each%20other.%20What%20I%20like%20about%20queer%20culture%20is%20that%20we%20somehow%20find%20a%20way%20to%20thrive%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Navin.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ETaking%20the%20straights%20to%20gay%20school.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EMy%20full%20special%20is%20here%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%