ent%22%3A231%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fluna-25-russia-starts-processing-data-from-moon-lander-hoping-to-make-history-12939352%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fluna-25-russia-starts-processing-data-from-moon-lander-hoping-to-make-history-12939352%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fluna-25-russia-starts-processing-data-from-moon-lander-hoping-to-make-history-12939352%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Newborn%20Delivered%20By%20Roadside%20Near%20Raj%20Bhavan%20In%20Lucknow%2C%20Dies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20four-and-a-half-month%20pregnant%20woman%20delivered%20her%20baby%20on%20the%20roadside%20near%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%20here%20on%20Sunday.%20The%20foetus%20was%20brought%20dead%20to%20a%20hospital%2C%20doctors%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20video%20of%20the%20incident%20surfaced%20on%20social%20media%20leading%20to%20a%20sharp%20reaction%20to%20the%20state%20of%20health%20services%20in%20UP%20from%20Samajwadi%20Party%20leader%20Shivpal%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUttar%20Pradesh%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Brajesh%20Pathak%2C%20who%20also%20holds%20the%20health%20portfolio%2C%20confirmed%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20taken%20cognizance%20of%20the%20incident%20and%20I%20am%20going%20to%20the%20spot.%20What%20I%20have%20been%20told%20by%20the%20principal%20secretary%20is%20that%20this%20family%20was%20going%20in%20a%20rickshaw%20and%20the%20incident%20took%20place%20near%20gate%20number%2013%20of%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20said%20when%20contacted%20by%20PTI%20initially.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20baby%20was%20taken%20to%20Veerangana%20Jhalkari%20Bai%20Women%20and%20Child%20Hospital%20where%20it%20was%20declared%20dead%20by%20doctors.%20It%20was%20later%20buried%20at%20Baikunth%20Dhaam%20in%20Lucknow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20doctor%20posted%20at%20the%20labour%20room%20of%20Veerangana%20Jhalkari%20Bai%20Women%20and%20Child%20Hospital%20told%20PTI%20that%20following%20the%20incident%2C%20the%20woman%2C%20Rupa%20Soni%2C%20underwent%20a%20check%20up%20at%20around%2012.30%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEarlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20she%20had%20gone%20to%20the%20Shyama%20Prasad%20Mukherjee%20(Civil)%20Hospital%20in%20Lucknow%20after%20experiencing%20pain%20and%20was%20administered%20an%20injection.%20She%20went%20home%20but%20did%20not%20get%20any%20relief%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20doctor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20on%20her%20way%20here%2C%20she%20delivered%20(the%20baby)%20outside%20Raj%20Bhavan.%20The%20baby%20was%20brought%20dead%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20doctor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrajesh%20Pathak%20said%20the%20woman%20decided%20to%20take%20a%20rickshaw%20and%20not%20an%20ambulance%20to%20the%20hospital%2C%20but%20when%20some%20passersby%20outside%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%20called%20an%20ambulance%2C%20it%20arrived%20in%2025%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20ambulance%20responded%20in%2025%20minutes.%20They%20(the%20family)%20had%20not%20sought%20an%20ambulance%20initially%20and%20took%20a%20rickshaw%2C%26quot%3B%20Brajesh%20Pathak%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShivpal%20Yadav%2C%20however%2C%20alleged%20that%20the%20incident%20occurred%20due%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bnon-availability%26quot%3B%20of%20an%20ambulance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20state's%20health%20system%20is%20on%20ventilator%20support%20despite%20lakhs%20of%20advertisements%20and%20claims.%20A%20pregnant%20woman%20going%20to%20the%20hospital%20by%20rickshaw%20was%20forced%20to%20deliver%20on%20the%20roadside%20near%20Raj%20Bhavan%20due%20to%20the%20non-availability%20of%20an%20ambulance.%20It%20is%20shameful%20for%20the%20entire%20system%20and%20it%20is%20the%20reality%20of%20the%20state's%20health%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20post%20in%20Hindi%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C