%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Heritage%20Building%20in%20Hyderabad%20Has%20Seen%20the%20World%E2%80%99s%20Most%20Significant%20Medical%20Breakthroughs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2027%2C%20the%20Telangana%20government%20submitted%20an%20affidavit%20before%20the%20Telangana%20High%20Court%20announcing%20its%20decision%20to%20demolish%20all%20buildings%20that%20form%20part%20of%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F98540%2Fcelebrating-100-years-osmania-university-alumni-adopt-villages%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Osmania%20General%20Hospital%20(OGH)%20%3C%2Fa%3Ecampus%20%E2%80%94%20including%20the%20heritage%20block.%20In%20its%20place%2C%20the%20government%20plans%20to%20build%20a%20new%201800-bed%20facility.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20are%20currently%20several%20public%20interest%20litigations%20(PIL)%20in%20the%20High%20Court%20that%20seek%20to%20preserve%20the%20heritage%20block.%C2%A0%20For%20instance%2C%20one%20filed%20by%20social%20activist%20Lubna%20Sarwath%20calls%20the%20demolition%20unconstitutional%20which%20will%20%E2%80%9Churt%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20identity%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20State%20cannot%20afford%20the%20luxury%20of%20forgetting%20that%20the%20destruction%20of%20heritage%20buildings%20will%20rob%20its%20people%20of%20the%20essence%20of%20their%20identity%2C%20and%20will%20deprive%20the%20city%20of%20its%20sense%20of%20uniqueness.%20While%20it%20is%20important%20to%20plan%20for%20the%20future%2C%20it%20is%20equally%20important%20to%20protect%2C%20to%20preserve%20and%20to%20promote%20the%20past%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sarwath%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExperts%20want%20to%20preserve%20the%20heritage%20building%2C%20and%20want%20the%20new%20hospital%20to%20either%20be%20built%20around%20it%2C%20or%20at%20another%20location.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20take%20a%20look%20at%20what%20makes%20this%20hospital%20so%20iconic.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHyderabad%E2%80%99s%20medical%20breakthroughs%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20724px)%20100vw%2C%20724px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fafzal-gunj-1691745063.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22724%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Afzal%20Gunj%20hospital%20was%20ravaged%20by%20the%20Musi%20floods%20in%201908%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fafzal-gunj-1691745063.jpg%20724w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fafzal-gunj-1691745063-300x221.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fafzal-gunj-1691745063-500x368.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fafzal-gunj-1691745063-150x110.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-327027%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22533%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20first%20international%20chloroform%20trials%20were%20held%20at%20the%20Afzal%20Gunj%20hospital.%20Image%3A%20The%20Deccan%20Archive%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20mid-19th%20century%2C%20medical%20education%20was%20picking%20up%20in%20Hyderabad%20with%20the%20advent%20of%20the%20Hyderabad%20Medical%20School.%20The%20land%20that%20houses%20the%20OGH%20campus%20today%20was%20earlier%20home%20to%20the%20Afzal%20Gunj%20Hospital%2C%20which%20was%20constructed%20in%201866%20and%20served%20as%20a%20teaching%20hospital.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20at%20these%20two%20buildings%20that%20major%20medical%20breakthroughs%20were%20made.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20discovery%20of%20malaria%20was%20made%20at%20the%20Hyderabad%20Medical%20School%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F272865%2Fhyderabad-fever-hospital-sir-ronald-ross-nobel-prize-malaria%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENobel%20laureate%20Sir%20Ronald%20Ross%3C%2Fa%3E.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Afzal%20Gunj%20Hospital%20contributed%20to%20a%20major%20breakthrough%20in%20anesthesia.%20The%20first%20international%20chloroform%20trials%2C%20backed%20by%20the%20sixth%20Nizam%20Mir%20Mahboob%20Ali%20Khan%2C%20took%20place%20in%20this%20hospital%20from%201888%20to%201891%2C%20and%20were%20conducted%20by%20his%20personal%20physician%20Dr%20Edward%20Lawrie.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chloroform%20Commission%20conducted%20experiments%20to%20establish%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20chloroform%20as%20an%20anesthetic%20to%20treat%20patients.%20It%20was%20a%20major%20breakthrough%20that%20led%20to%20several%20lives%20being%20saved%20in%20the%20future.%20While%20the%20chemical%20was%20being%20used%20for%20surgical%20procedures%2C%20this%20trial%20helped%20in%20determining%20how%20it%20could%20be%20used%20safely.%20The%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20report%20would%20go%20on%20to%20be%20published%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Lancet%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilt%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20floods%20and%20a%20plague%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FUntitled-design-2023-08-11T143636.627-1691745341.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20tamarind%20tree%20that%20saved%20the%20lives%20of%20150%20people%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FUntitled-design-2023-08-11T143636.627-1691745341.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FUntitled-design-2023-08-11T143636.627-1691745341-